description: If you’re craving some Southern comfort and some Asian scrumptiousness, Peached Tortilla is totally the truck for you. With a mission to add new flavors, new ideas, and new feelings (like “peached”: flavor-smitten) to the Austin foodie scene, this culinary team is taking the best of Japan and Atlanta cuisines, and dishing out some mighty tasty fusion food.  Their mouthwatering selection includes the JapaJam Burger (⅓ lb all-beef patty, sweet tomato jam, jalapeño jack cheese, fried egg, Japanese BBQ sauce, and topped with crispy tempura beer battered onion strings), the Pad Thai Taco (chili garlic-marinated chicken, stir fried in pad thai sauce, scrambled eggs, mixed veggies, all in a warm tortilla), Bacon Jam Fries, a delectable variety of Cake Pops, and much more. So if you’re feeling pretty hungry, you better come out to this truck and get peached real soon.
name: The Peached Tortilla
